iends of Jane Addams College of Social Work, where you can connect with your alma mater, with students and with one another.           IGNITE the Future of Social Work  On October 28, 2017, UIC kicked off its five-year IGNITE campaign with a goal of raising $750,000,000 in support of students, faculty, research and connections with the community.  Jane Addams College of Social Work is fully committed to IGNITE the future of social work by raising $4 million in support of it’s strategic priorities, especially scholarships for deserving students.   INGITE the Future             Connect & Engage  Connect with the college, with other JACSW alumni, and with currently enrolled students.   Connect & Engage             Alumni Events  The annual Alumni & Friends Celebration and other events for alumni and friends of the college.   Alumni Events             Alumni Updates  A round-up of news and updates from alumni of Jane Addams College of Social Work.   Alumni Updates             Alumni Awards  Information about the Jane Addams Distinguished Alumni Achievement Award and Rising Alumni Award, and how to nominate your fellow alumni for these honors.   Alumni Awards             LSW/LCSW Information  Video presentation and additional information about LSW/LCSW licensure in Illinois.   Licensure Information            Alumni & Friends    Back to main content           Make a Gift Now    IGNITE Campaign: Make Your Impact    Where & How to Give    Connect & Engage     Update Your Information    What's New With You?    Engage With Students    Alumni & Friends Newsletter      Alumni Events & Awards     Award Nominations      Alumni Updates    LSW/LCSW Information              Jane Addams College of Social Work  UI Health                        UIC's seven health sciences colleges and health care delivery enterprise.       Footer Menu 4    For Prospective Students    Apply Now    Alumni & Friends    Make a Gift Now    Current Students & Faculty         Contact   MSW Admissions  1040 W